author: fdmanana
msg: _all_docs rows must not deleted include documents
After COUCHDB-1061, when POSTing to _all_docs?include_docs=true with
the body "keys" option, deleted documents were part part of the output.
The "doc" property of each _all_docs row should have the value 'null'
A test was added to help prevent this from happening again.

author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Martin Kreidenweis "New Custom Method order ID generation implementation in OFBIZ-3765 broke backwards compatibility" (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-4178) - OFBIZ-4178

Due to missed col-name attributes for the deprecated field names (old* fields) and a typo in the minilang code in the original patch (OFBIZ-3765), the backwards compatibility with the old enum IDs broke.
